data.description: Excellent 3 Bedroom 2.5 Bath home on a Spacious Corner Lot with Private Fenced Backyard and pergola-covered patio. Ideal location! Low maintenance living less than 5 minutes from I-575! Hardwood throughout the main level of this open floor plan. Open Kitchen features rich wood cabinets, tile backsplash, and gas cooking plus refrigerator. Upstairs owner's suite has a private bath and generous walk-in closet. Two spacious secondary bedrooms and a hall bath with laundry complete the upstairs. The home has been well maintained with walls freshly painted and the new carpet. Community features sidewalks, pool, playground, pocket parks including a tot lot across the street from the house. Close to retailers, restaurants, and one exit to Northside Cherokee Hospital!
